data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Portland, TX. This well-maintained property offers an open floor plan, spacious living area with tray ceilings, the kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a fourth room that could be used as an office, and a tranquil backyard oasis perfect for relaxation or entertaining. This beautiful home is located approximately 1 mile from the high school, and approximately 3 minutes from the sports complex. Schedule your private tour today!
